round-end-system-round-restart-eta-announcement-carp = Round will restart in {$time} {$units}...
  { $eorg ->
    [true] End-of-Round Griefing is now allowed until the round restarts.
    Roleplay rules are no longer required to be followed.
    Core rules must still be followed.
    Have fun and go wild until the round restart.
    *[false] End-of-Round Griefing is NOT allowed.
    Roleplay rules are still required to be followed.
    All normal conduct rules remain in effect until the round restarts.
    Please continue to roleplay appropriately.
  }
